INSERT INTO `cm_article` VALUES ('8a3080d54c406b73014c5108b03b0589', null, 'Google Nexus', null, '<div><b>Introduce</b>&nbsp;</div><div>The <u>Nexus One</u> was manufactured by HTC and released in January 2010 as the first Nexus phone. It was released with Android 2.1 Eclair, and was updated in May 2010 to be the first phone with Android 2.2 Froyo. The <u>Nexus S</u>, manufactured by Samsung, was released in December 2010 to coincide with the release of Android 2.3 Gingerbread. In December 2011 it was updated to Android 4.0 Ice Cream Sandwich.The <u>Galaxy Nexus</u>, manufactured by Samsung, was released in November 2011 (GSM version, US released on Verizon 15 December 2011) to coincide with the release of Android 4.0 Ice Cream Sandwich. It was upgraded to Android software 4.3 (Jelly Bean) in July 2013. The <u>Nexus 4</u> is a smartphone in the Google Nexus line, released in November 2012 and manufactured by LG. It was the first Android device that used Android\'s 4.2 Jelly Bean update version. It was updated to Android 4.3 in June 2013 and to Android 4.4 in November 2013. The <u>Nexus 5</u> is a smartphone in the Google Nexus line. It was posted for sale on the Google Play store for $349 on October 31, 2013. It is again manufactured by LG. It is the first Android device using Android 4.4 KitKat.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><b>Review Video :</b></div><div><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dg2UIzIt4s\">Nexus 5 review</a><br></div><div><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zFOnOLXrMBQ\">Nexus 4 Review</a></div><div><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fFRl2oOqDsk\">Samsung Galaxy Nexus Review</a></div><div><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b7om8bnfNnk\">Google Nexus S Review</a><br></div><div><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oZGEUcDspIo\">HTC Nexus One Review</a><br><p></p><div><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/1dg2UIzIt4s?wmode=opaque\" data-youtube-id=\"1dg2UIzIt4s\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><br><p></p><p style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><br></b></p><p style=\"line-height: 26px; \"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/zFOnOLXrMBQ?wmode=opaque\" data-youtube-id=\"zFOnOLXrMBQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><br></b></p><p style=\"line-height: 26px; \"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><br></b></p><p style=\" line-height: 26px;\"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/fFRl2oOqDsk?wmode=opaque\" data-youtube-id=\"fFRl2oOqDsk\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><br></b></p><p style=\" line-height: 26px;\"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><br></b></p><p style=\" line-height: 26px;\"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/b7om8bnfNnk?wmode=opaque\" data-youtube-id=\"b7om8bnfNnk\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><br></b></p><p style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><br></b></p><p style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><b style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/oZGEUcDspIo?wmode=opaque\" data-youtube-id=\"oZGEUcDspIo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><span id=\"sceditor-end-marker\" class=\"sceditor-selection sceditor-ignore\" style=\"line-height: 0; display: none;\"></span><span id=\"sceditor-start-marker\" class=\"sced